        <item>
                <title>高三学生绝对真实的写照</title>
                <description>&lt;p&gt;高3.刚开学：[](http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358887.gif)&lt;a href=&quot;http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358887.gif&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358887.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;   开学一周后：[](http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358909.gif)&lt;a href=&quot;http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358909.gif&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358909.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;  开学两周后：[](http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358911.gif)&lt;a href=&quot;http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358911.gif&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://img1.qq.com/edu/pics/5358/5358911.gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
